-- ds.page: payment-success
id: payment-success-api

-- ds.markdown:

This API will deploy the user package at fly.io
(through [create-instance](id: create-instance-api) procedure) and
then it will redirect to the payment success page.

It requires certain parameters listed below.

- plan
- package-name
- base-url

URL: `<service-endpoint>/api/payment-success/`

Request Type: `GET`